;============================================================
;============================================================
;=====================FLEXCURVE SECTION======================
;============================================================
;============================================================
;============================================================
;===========================MIS A1===========================
;============================================================
;MIS perpetuation and anchor stability {
	:Primary Anchor {
		;Blank {
			;Prevent ortho stub, straight and T into curve {
				0x5ca60000,0,0,0x57000100,1,0=0,0,0,0,0,0 ;Stub
				0x5ca60000,0,0,0x57000000,1,0=0,0,0,0,0,0 ;Ortho
				0x5ca60000,0,0,0x57000000,3,0=0,0,0,0,0,0 ;Ortho
				0x5ca60000,0,0,0x57600400,1,0=0,0,0,0,0,0 ;T
				0x5ca60000,0,0,0x57600400,2,0=0,0,0,0,0,0 ;T
				0x5ca60000,0,0,0x57600400,3,0=0,0,0,0,0,0 ;T
			;}
			;Continue MIS drag out of curve {
				0x5ca60000,2,0,0x57000100,1,0=0x5ca60000,2,0,0x57020100,3,1 ;MIS stub
				0x5ca60000,2,0,0x57000000,1,0=0x5ca60000,2,0,0x57020000,3,0 ;MIS ortho
				0x5ca60000,2,0,0x57000000,3,0=0x5ca60000,2,0,0x57020000,3,0 ;MIS ortho
				;Adjacent overpasses
				0x5ca60000,2,0,0x57201A00,1,0=0x5ca60000,2,0,0x57201C00,3,0 ;ERHW-2 over RHW-2 -> ERHW-2 over MIS
				0x5ca60000,2,0,0x57201A00,3,0=0x5ca60000,2,0,0x57201C00,3,0 ;ERHW-2 over RHW-2 -> ERHW-2 over MIS
				0x5ca60000,2,0,0x57221A00,3,0=0x5ca60000,2,0,0x57221C00,3,1 ;EMIS over RHW-2 -> EMIS over MIS (Yellow toward curve)

;===========================MIS A2===========================
;============================================================
;MIS perpetuation and anchor stability {
	:Primary Anchor {
		;Blank {
			;Prevent ortho stub, straight and T into curve {
				0x5ca61000,0,0,0x57000100,1,0=0,0,0,0,0,0 ;Stub
				0x5ca61000,0,0,0x57000000,1,0=0,0,0,0,0,0 ;Ortho
				0x5ca61000,0,0,0x57000000,3,0=0,0,0,0,0,0 ;Ortho
				0x5ca61000,0,0,0x57600400,1,0=0,0,0,0,0,0 ;T
				0x5ca61000,0,0,0x57600400,2,0=0,0,0,0,0,0 ;T
				0x5ca61000,0,0,0x57600400,3,0=0,0,0,0,0,0 ;T
			;}
			;Continue MIS drag out of curve {
				0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57000100,1,0=0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57020100,1,0 ;MIS stub
				0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57000000,1,0=0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57020000,1,0 ;MIS ortho
				0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57000000,3,0=0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57020000,1,0 ;MIS ortho
				;Adjacent overpasses
				0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57201A00,1,0=0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57201C00,1,0 ;ERHW-2 over RHW-2 -> ERHW-2 over MIS
				0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57201A00,3,0=0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57201C00,1,0 ;ERHW-2 over RHW-2 -> ERHW-2 over MIS
				0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57221A00,3,0=0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57221C00,1,0 ;EMIS over RHW-2 -> EMIS over MIS (Yellow toward curve)
				0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57221A00,1,0=0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57221C00,1,1 ;EMIS over RHW-2 -> EMIS over MIS (White toward curve)
				0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57231A00,3,0=0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57231C00,1,0 ;ERHW-4 over RHW-2 -> ERHW-4 over MIS (Yellow toward curve)
				0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57231A00,1,0=0x5ca61000,2,0,0x57231C00,1,1 ;ERHW-4 over RHW-2 -> ERHW-4 over MIS (White toward curve)
